title: Zdrava jidelna Spirala
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Macrobiotic, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Daily menu consists of 4 main meals 2 side meals, a vegetable salad, and a dessert. There are 4 menu options, a vegetarian, organic meat, or a daily discounted menu (soup, main  meal, side meal). Fresh squeezed juices, cooking from seasonal vegetables and fruit, healthy meals for children, gluten-free options. Everything is clearly labeled. Honey and syrups (maple, corn, date) used as sweeteners. Nice atmosphere, has Wi-Fi.
